    <item>
      <title>Timber Logistics Stock-on-Hand Forecasting Dashboard</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/projects/stock-on-hand/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/projects/stock-on-hand/</guid>
      
        <description>&lt;p&gt;This project presents a Power BI dashboard for dynamic short-term stock forecasting across timber transportation phases.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/files/stock-on-hand/stock-on-hand.pbix&#34; download class=&#34;download-btn&#34;&gt;
  Download .pbix file
&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;pbix-version&#34;&gt;Created in Power BI Desktop 2.150.1704.0 64-bit (January 2026)&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;portfolio-carousel&#34; id=&#34;stock-on-hand-carousel&#34;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;carousel-track&#34;&gt;
    &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/projects/stock-on-hand/01.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Timber logistics dashboard screenshot 1&#34;&gt;
    &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/projects/stock-on-hand/02.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Timber logistics dashboard screenshot 2&#34;&gt;
    &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/projects/stock-on-hand/03.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Timber logistics dashboard screenshot 3&#34;&gt;
    &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/projects/stock-on-hand/04.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Timber logistics dashboard screenshot 4&#34;&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;carousel-nav&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;false&#34;&gt;
    &lt;button type=&#34;button&#34; class=&#34;carousel-btn prev&#34; aria-label=&#34;Previous image&#34;&gt;‹&lt;/button&gt;
    &lt;button type=&#34;button&#34; class=&#34;carousel-btn next&#34; aria-label=&#34;Next image&#34;&gt;›&lt;/button&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;-overview&#34;&gt;📌 Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This Power BI dashboard supports dynamic stock-on-hand forecasting across timber transportation phases for a large forestry holding company. It helps logistics managers evaluate short-term inventory trends, test how well a linear model fits observed stock dynamics, and estimate when inventory may run out under the currently selected conditions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>The Port Authority of New York and New Jersey Traffic Dashboard</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/projects/panynj-traffic-dashboard/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/projects/panynj-traffic-dashboard/</guid>
      
        <description>&lt;p&gt;This project presents a Power BI dashboard built on public Port Authority traffic data.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/files/panynj/PANYNJ-Traffic-Dashboard.pbix&#34; download class=&#34;download-btn&#34;&gt;
  Download .pbix file
&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;pbix-version&#34;&gt;Created in Power BI Desktop 2.150.1704.0 64-bit (January 2026)&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;portfolio-carousel&#34; id=&#34;panynj-carousel&#34;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;carousel-track&#34;&gt;
    &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/projects/panynj/01.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;PANYNJ dashboard screenshot 1&#34;&gt;
    &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/projects/panynj/02.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;PANYNJ dashboard screenshot 2&#34;&gt;
    &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/projects/panynj/03.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;PANYNJ dashboard screenshot 3&#34;&gt;
    &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/projects/panynj/04.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;PANYNJ dashboard screenshot 4&#34;&gt;
    &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/projects/panynj/05.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;PANYNJ dashboard screenshot 5&#34;&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;carousel-nav&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;false&#34;&gt;
    &lt;button type=&#34;button&#34; class=&#34;carousel-btn prev&#34; aria-label=&#34;Previous image&#34;&gt;‹&lt;/button&gt;
    &lt;button type=&#34;button&#34; class=&#34;carousel-btn next&#34; aria-label=&#34;Next image&#34;&gt;›&lt;/button&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;-overview&#34;&gt;📌 Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This Power BI dashboard analyzes monthly traffic volume and E-ZPass usage across six major Port Authority crossings between New York and New Jersey. It consolidates public monthly reports into a single analytical model and makes it easier to explore long-term trends, facility-level differences, and changes in transponder adoption over time.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
