  &lt;iframe
    src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/files/Nikolai_Shchelkov_Resume.pdf&#34;
    class=&#34;resume-preview&#34;
    title=&#34;Nikolai Shchelkov Resume PDF&#34;
  &gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;profile-of-achievements-in-key-figures&#34;&gt;Profile of Achievements in Key Figures&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul class=&#34;resume-highlights&#34;&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;🎓 &lt;strong&gt;3 advanced degrees with honors&lt;/strong&gt; — two STEM degrees and one MBA, with one earned in Russia and two in the United States; currently pursuing a PhD at Florida Atlantic University and inducted into the Phi Kappa Phi Honor Society through the Eastern New Mexico University chapter.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;📊 &lt;strong&gt;14 years of contributions&lt;/strong&gt; in data analytics, emerging technologies, and digital skills gap reduction.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;🗽 &lt;strong&gt;3 years of meaningful contributions in the U.S.&lt;/strong&gt; across California, New York, and New Mexico, recognized through academic awards and strong support from respected local experts.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;🏭 &lt;strong&gt;Impact across 4 industries&lt;/strong&gt; — logistics and transportation, oil and gas, timber, and nonprofit — with models and dashboards used daily by hundreds of peers and stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;🛠️ &lt;strong&gt;6 core analytical tools and dozens of supporting frameworks&lt;/strong&gt; implemented, including a candidate nationwide standard for business process notation, portfolio optimization models, customer insight quantification techniques, startup evaluation templates, dynamic reporting systems, and a comprehensive AI implementation framework.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;🏆 &lt;strong&gt;2 major academic distinctions&lt;/strong&gt; — one top-level academic award in Russia and one significant award in the United States, both earned in highly competitive environments.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;📝 &lt;strong&gt;30+ innovative business plans and 250+ grant applications&lt;/strong&gt; evaluated as an invited expert for national foundations.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;📚 &lt;strong&gt;7,000+ unique views&lt;/strong&gt; of published articles on a leading Russian-language blog focused on Power BI and data analytics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
      
